tweet: Shootings in places of worship are becoming too commonplace. People should not be afraid to gather and fellowship. I thank the parishioners who acted selflessly to save lives. Our hearts go out to the victims' families and members of the West Freeway Church of Christ.

Happy Birthday Texas!
December 29, 1845, Texas was the 28th state admitted to the Union! Celebrate by exploring maps of the Lone Star State online at The Library of Congress.  
#Texas #Maps #LibraryofCongress

I am proud to announce that the U.S. Department of Health & Human Services has awarded $1,397,132 to the Martin Luther King, Jr. Family Clinic. This clinic provides vital health services and programs to thousands of Dallas-Ft. Worth families.
